OL,7,FAn exhibition celebrating the life of
OL,8,Fone of Rugby Union's true legends has
OL,9,Fgone on display to mark 100 years
OL,10,Fsince his birth.
OL,12,FFor almost 50 years Hawick's Bill
OL,13,FMcLaren commentated on the game for
OL,14,Fboth radio and television. He was
OL,15,Fknown for his inimitable way with
OL,16,Fwords and in 2015, five years after
OL,17,Fhis death, he became the first non-
OL,18,Fplayer to be inducted into World
OL,19,FRugby's Hall of Fame.
OL,3,CHawick Museum exhibition tells life
OL,4,Cstory of rugby commentator Bill
OL,5,CMcLaren
